    "Moreover, although this paper is mainly about measurement, we lay the groundwork for exploring relationships of the presented indices with various other variables.",
    "For instance, further research can examine how political variables specific to democratic and autocratic regimes, such as the impact of ideologically extreme governments, weak coalitions and military coups influence these indices.",
